    "name": "Aksun",
    "steam_appid": 3129360,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129360/extras/aa8f38eb047db92958462661bd330e09.avif?t=1770974594\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129360/extras_big/aa8f38eb047db92958462661bd330e09.avif?t=1770974594 width=800 height=596 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Aksun</strong> 是一款以韩国巫觋信仰为基础的动作砍杀 Roguelite 游戏。你被困在名为「棺」的诅咒封印装置中，这是为了封印堕落教团的意志与其怪物先知而打造的。每次挑战都会将你更深入地拖入记忆、痛苦与转生的循环之中，同时也让你更加精通。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129360/extras/ef3e484439ba9fdccd6dd95acc058e10.avif?t=1770974594\" width=800 height=380 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>跳入 Aksun 的封印</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <strong>Aksun</strong> 中，死亡只是仪式的一部分，每一次胜利都会揭开真相的一层面纱。你被困于 <strong>Aksun</strong> 的封印之中，那是一座由破碎轮回所构成的诅咒牢狱。你将唤醒失落的武器、吸收腐化的鬼物，在这个记得你每一次尝试的世界中战斗突围。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>三重结构的构筑系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Aksun</strong> 的成长系统是由三大核心要素之间的互动所构成：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>武器</strong>：与地狱之神绑定，定义你的战斗风格，并解锁强大的觉醒技能。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>鬼物</strong>：教团仪式的残留结晶，带来元素效果、召唤与混沌之力。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>灵气</strong>：基于共鸣的属性修正项，让所有要素组合成多层次且无法预测的构筑。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129360/extras/d38e4e0d94f933ba10445c634b1a9061.poster.avif?t=1770974594\" width=800 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129360/extras/d38e4e0d94f933ba10445c634b1a9061.webm?t=1770974594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129360/extras/d38e4e0d94f933ba10445c634b1a9061.mp4?t=1770974594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌握这三种系统之间的关系，是在循环中生存，并最终打破它的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129360/extras/ccb004eecbbd9248b43dd579bc5874e1.poster.avif?t=1770974594\" width=800 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129360/extras/ccb004eecbbd9248b43dd579bc5874e1.webm?t=1770974594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>相克的五行</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个鬼物都属于五行之一——火、冰、风、土或雷，并不会单独发挥完整力量。当它们彼此结合时，将触发毁灭性的连锁反应：火焰点燃风暴，雷电击穿熔岩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129360/extras/4b9b11c36ddded76ab8ad8e396a6eabd.poster.avif?t=1770974594\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129360/extras/4b9b11c36ddded76ab8ad8e396a6eabd.webm?t=1770974594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129360/extras/4b9b11c36ddded76ab8ad8e396a6eabd.mp4?t=1770974594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>全新构筑，全新挑战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个章节都是由分支节点构成的地图。每完成一个关卡，你可以选择接下来的路线与奖励：通过共鸣强化武器、获得新的鬼物共鸣、解锁觉醒被动技能、收集灵气调整属性，或是冒险购买高风险的强化道具。每次死亡都会重置你的装备构成，但每次挑战都会让你更接近更聪明、更致命的组合，并以无法预测的方式演化你的构筑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129360/extras/64b19a619157adf63f7aab713eda9789.avif?t=1770974594\" width=800 height=120 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>渗透进游戏的世界观</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >整个游戏发生在扭曲的六道轮回回声中，那是一个为了惩罚拒绝轮回者而设计的封闭循环。曾是教团首领的木头鬼王，如今成为其中最破碎的囚徒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从系统到象征，每个设计都扎根于韩国神话、仪式与灵性信仰之中，包括巫觋信仰、五行平衡、神罚与祖灵记忆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这不只是神话，而是一场以鲜血完成的仪式。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129360/extras/ea94cf50b1b3ee68074a26faf8f049bc.avif?t=1770974594\" width=800 height=120 /></span></p>",
